erals660x100.png?t=1505758720\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mobs</h2>Mobs are the part of the Planet\u2019s Environment. They are full of substances and materials that you will not find anywhere else, so hunting them down can benefit.<br><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/681750/extras/Monsters620x182.png?t=1505758720\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Crafting</h2>Crafting is one of the most important things while living on the Unknown Planet. Use special tables to create new things.<br><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/681750/extras/Crafting620x182.png?t=1505758720\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Melting</h2>It is the process of heat treatment of resources.<br><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/681750/extras/Melting620x182.png?t=1505758720\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Crushing</h2>It is the process of crushing resources in order to reduce the size or change the form of them.<br><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/681750/extras/Crushing620x182.png?t=1505758720\"><br><br><br>Feel free to contact me:<br><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Voxelaxy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >https://www.facebook.com/Voxelaxy/</a><br><a href=\"https://twitter.com/jklementewicz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >https://twitter.com/jklementewicz</a>", "mac_requirements": [], "background": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/681750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1505758720", "movies": [{"webm": {"480": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693586/movie480.webm?t=1503525303", "max": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693586/movie_max.webm?t=1503525303"}, "name": "Voxelaxy Trailer 1", "thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256693586/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1503525303", "highlight": true, "id": 256693586}], "screenshots": [{"path_thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/681750/ss_de6c66d9dda391d00835b85b89310b54acb5c36b.600x338.jpg?t=15057587